<div class="pd-dragpanel-documentation">

	<section id="overview">
		<h2 class="doc-section">Overview</h2>
		<p>
			<code>PDDragPanel</code> enables drag-and-drop reordering of items in a list.
			Works with <code>PDDragContainer</code> to manage item order and selection.
		</p>
	</section>

	<section id="quick-start">
		<h2 class="doc-section">Quick Start</h2>

